<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ATC Africa Newsletter</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f1f1f;
            background-color: #f6f7f9;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e6e7eb;
        }
        
        .header {
            background-color: #4b0082;
            padding: 32px 28px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #3e006e;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 28px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting h2 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .greeting p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .newsletter-date {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
        }
        
        .newsletter-date p {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .section h3 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .section h3::before {
            content: "";
            width: 4px;
            height: 16px;
            background-color: #4b0082;
            margin-right: 8px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        
        .event-card {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
        }
        
        .event-card h4 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .event-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .event-meta span {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .event-meta span::before {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
        
        .event-meta .date::before { content: ""; }
        .event-meta .time::before { content: ""; }
        .event-meta .location::before { content: ""; }
        .event-meta .category::before { content: ""; }
        
        .event-description {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .event-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4b0082;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .event-link:hover {
            background-color: #3e006e;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            background-color: #f7f8fc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
        }
        
        .cta-section h3 {
            color: #1f1f1f;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .cta-section p {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4b0082;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #3e006e;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #fafbfc;
            padding: 24px 28px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eceef2;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #566074;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #4b0082;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #3e006e;
        }
        
        .unsubscribe {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .unsubscribe a {
            color: #6c757d;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            color: #4b0082;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ATC Africa Newsletter</h1>
            <p>Monthly update from Africa's tech community</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                <h2>Hello <span class="highlight"><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></span>!</h2>
                <p>Welcome to your monthly ATC Africa newsletter! Here's what's happening in Africa's vibrant tech community this month.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="newsletter-date">
                <p>📅 Newsletter Issue: <%= newsletterDate %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h3>🎉 Community Highlights</h3>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number"><%= totalEvents %></div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Events This Month</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number"><%= newMembers %></div>
                        <div class="stat-label">New Members</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number"><%= totalSpeakers %></div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Featured Speakers</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number"><%= totalSponsors %></div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Active Sponsors</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h3>🔥 Featured Events</h3>
                <% if (featuredEvents && featuredEvents.length > 0) { %>
                    <% featuredEvents.forEach(event => { %>
                        <div class="event-card">
                            <h4><%= event.title %></h4>
                            <div class="event-meta">
                                <span class="date"><%= event.date %></span>
                                <span class="time"><%= event.time %></span>
                                <span class="location"><%= event.location %></span>
                                <span class="category"><%= event.category %></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="event-description">
                                <%= event.description %>
                            </div>
                            <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>/events/<%= event.id %>" class="event-link">Learn More</a>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-style: italic;">No featured events this month. Check back soon!</p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
            
            <div class="section">
                <h3>💡 Tech Insights</h3>
                <p>Stay ahead with the latest trends and insights from Africa's tech ecosystem:</p>
                <ul style="color: #555; margin-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Emerging technologies shaping Africa's digital future</li>
                    <li>Success stories from African tech entrepreneurs</li>
                    <li>Investment opportunities in the African tech space</li>
                    <li>Skills development and career opportunities</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h3>🚀 Get Involved!</h3>
                <p>Don't miss out on the amazing opportunities in Africa's tech community. Join us in building the future!</p>
                <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>" class="cta-button">Explore ATC Africa</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px;">
                Have an event to share? Submit it to our platform and reach thousands of tech enthusiasts!
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong><%= companyName %></strong></p>
            <p>Connecting Africa's Tech Community</p>
            <p>📍 <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>"><%= websiteUrl %></a></p>
            <p>📧 <a href="mailto:<%= companyEmail %>"><%= companyEmail %></a></p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Twitter</a> |
                <a href="#">LinkedIn</a> |
                <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="#">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="unsubscribe">
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeLink %>">Unsubscribe from this newsletter</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd;">
                © <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.<br>
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you have any questions, please contact us at <%= supportEmail %>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 